1. The human BRCA2 gene has 15 splice variants.
2. The longest splice variant ENST00000470094.2, at 12077 bp, has 28 exons.
3. There are 27 introns in the longest splice variant mentioned above.
4. This gene is located on the Chromosome 13:32, 315, 508-32, 400, 265.
5. The gene synonyms of BRCA2 are BRCC2, FACD, FAD, FAD1, FANCD, FANCD1, and XRCC11.
6. There is one ortholog of human BRCA2 in the African Ostrich.
7. GCTCCTGGTTGTCTACCCATGGACCCAGAGGTTCTTTGACAGCTTTGGCAACCTGTCCTC
